SUBM_DATA_DO_NOT_MATCH_EXERCISE

public static final ExerciseException.ErrorType SUBM_DATA_DO_NOT_MATCH_EXERCISE
This type should be used in the unlikely event that a Executor or SubmissionVisualizer is tried to be loaded with SubmissionInfo data that does not match the ExerciseData in use. This happens if the exercise is changed after the submission is done in such a way that makes it essentially a new exercise-instance.
